{"tid":1541472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［就輸喇！］搞個白宮聯署，話俾侵侵知港共政府信唔過！","createTime":"2019-09-04T14:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T01:13:28.000Z","uid":304589,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fad25613527edd21dea242472c8c8004e542981f","tid":1541472,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"有冇得諗<br />\n<br />\n今日柒婆話動議撤回修例，相信大家都知港共政府係講緊語言偽術，但外國並唔係咁諗，近近地就講台灣，小弟有個台灣朋友cap圖問我係咪真係撤回，我解釋左一輪佢先明白原來未係真架！<br />\n<br />\n我再解釋呢幾個月以黎香港人爭取嘅係「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求」</span></strong>，唔撚再只係撤回送中！<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要俾外國，尤其係美帝知呢個唔係事實，未endgame架！！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要繼續推9/9復會後通過香港人權及民主法案</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲英文好，可以幫手寫寫，不勝感激！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！！！"},{"pid":"e665917e39b463d58402ad89ab6874ea12b73087","tid":1541472,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"［核彈］政府撤例，建制無能，白票洩憤，射比對家都唔益建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541383</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"218ee6883bc2cdf3ff32adf42fd1e2e289e7ed98","tid":1541472,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca78d7af88208ff3831e083059197abcc2071900","tid":1541472,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TodU6i9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTodU6i9.jpg&h=6f8854f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b4a31915e6be9f4f8c6b9647a2c6af797b3f7e2","tid":1541472,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"P牌推！"},{"pid":"3531dc6132b11ddac03b14d8798f87aeb979ae20","tid":1541472,"uid":41364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"Don't trust China<br />\nChina is Asshole<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywmzmSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywmzmSL.jpg&h=6d84c041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cad83ea89b51cf55851beef9b5b7da018a7e76c","tid":1541472,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0859daf85c1e1dfbd3a6bc5b6b528994d8a7d1","tid":1541472,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"push!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8f0f6722fb5799d477250db567d6bba3ec0abc","tid":1541472,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Qq01U3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Qq01U3.jpg&h=9448c0c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"452d64ef887783aab2990035771f44680f493e5b","tid":1541472,"uid":186414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"推到有文宣組搞聯署，利申英文得E"},{"pid":"c65ad0120d4a74a3ac6a80b95383617ad0399412","tid":1541472,"uid":287218,"like":0,"d